kground-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 仿宋;\">11月28日，机关党委举办党的十九届四中全会精神中心组（扩大）学习暨红色讲堂专题讲座，邀请中国人事科学研究院原常务副院长吴德贵教授作题为《深入学习贯彻党的十九届四中全会精神》辅导讲座，机关党员150余人参加讲座。</span></p>\n<div class=\"fck_uploadpics\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 21.3333px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: #333333; line-height: 28.8px; text-indent: 28px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: #333333; line-height: 28.8px; text-indent: 28px;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\" src=\"https://www.ccccltd.cn/ddjs/gzdt/201911/W020191128667379909562.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"553\" height=\"369\" /></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: #333333; line-height: 28.8px; text-indent: 32pt; overflow-x: hidden; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: #333333; line-height: 28.8px; text-indent: 32pt; overflow-x: hidden; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋;\">吴德贵教授围绕<span style=\"font-family: 仿宋;\">&ldquo;充分认识坚持和完善中国特色社会主义制度，推进国家治理体系和治理能力现代化的重大意义；深刻领会中国特色社会主义制度和国家治理体系的显著优势，坚持中国特色社会主义制度自信；准确把握坚持和完善中国特色社会主义制度，推进国家治理体系和治理能力现代化的总体要求、总体目标和重点任务和加强党的领导，确保全会确定的各项目标任务全面落实到位&rdquo;四个方面，深入浅出地阐释了十九届四中全会的重大精神，授课条理清晰、语言生动，受到机关党员干部好评。</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"TRS_PreAppend\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: #333333; line-height: 28.8px; text-indent: 28px; overflow-x: hidden; word-break: break-all;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: #333333; line-height: 28.8px; text-indent: 32pt; overflow-x: hidden; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋;\">参学同志纷纷表示，这次讲座主题鲜明、内容丰富，重点突出、阐释深刻，理论性和实践性都很强。机关党委书记刘俊华在总结讲话中强调，机关全体党员干部职工要把思想和行动统一到四中全会的要求部署上来，尤其是把其中深化国有企业改革，完善中国特色现代企业制度的有关要求落到工作的各领域、各方面、各环节，以主动自觉的学习热情，把学习四中全会精神与深入学习习近平新时代中国特色社会主义思想结合起来，与深入开展</span>&ldquo;不忘初心、牢记使命&rdquo;主题教育结合起来，努力做到学得更深、悟得更透，承担好党中央、习近平总书记赋予的政治责任，不断开创机关党委工作新局面，为率先建成世界一流企业努力奋斗。</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: #333333; line-height: 28.8px; text-indent: 32pt; overflow-x: hidden; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: #333333; line-height: 28.8px; text-indent: 28px;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\" src=\"https://www.ccccltd.cn/ddjs/gzdt/201911/W020191128667379903545.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"553\" height=\"369\" /></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: bas